<h2>Exec_Instance</h2>
<hr>
<p>Description of a SW task instance used to create the Application SW</p>

<p>General Attributes :</p>
<pre>
<li>name      [Mandatory]: Name of the SW executable instance </li>
<li>component [Mandatory]: Name of SW executable component</li>
<li>resource  [Optional]: HW resource where the task will run (HW_Instance or Computing_Group). If <li>os        [Optional]: OS where the task will run. If no Resource is defined it is mandatory   no OS is defined it is mandatory  </li>
<li>arguments [Optional]: List of arguments the task will receive at startup  </li>
<li>policy    [Optional]: Policy of the new task </li>
<li>priority  [Optional]: Priority of the new task  </li>
</li>
</pre>

<p>Structure:</p>

<pre>
&lt; Exec_Instance name="my_task" component="task_1" resource="node0" arguments="-s -t -f file"/ &gt;
	
</pre>

